Package com.revature.dao

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PokemonDao
    An interface that defines how the pokemon dao will work and what its jobs are and how to use this dao
    TradeDao
    Interface for the tradeDao that repersents the tasks to be accomplished and establishes the way to talk to this dao
    UserDao
    Interface to use the underlining SQL dao to manage user data
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PokemonDaoSql
    Pokemon DAO which handles the pokemon data.
    TradeDaoSql
    This dao handles all the transactions of trade requests for PokemonMania
    UserDaoSql
    Handles the saving and fetching of user data with the remote SQL database on AWS.
